Tomorrowland presents: Love Tomorrow Conference 2024. Prepare to explore the intersection of consciousness, innovation and entertainment as passionate people share their visions for a better, bolder, sustainable future on July 25. A day filled with keynote speeches, DJ sets, awe-inspiring live acts, a job fair and so much more. A limited amount of early bird tickets is now available, go to your Tomorrowland account or create one at my.tomorrowland.com.

Tomorrowland presents: ‘The Great Library of Tomorrow’. A unique immersive audiovisual experience for all ages in the heart of Barcelona, redefining the magic of Tomorrowland. 

Due to success extended until May 5, to celebrate you can buy tickets at a special price with the code ‘CELEBRATION’ for the period April-May. Code only available till March 10. 
More info at thegreatlibraryoftomorrow.com

@rogervandamme, Michellin-starred pastry chef, brought a visit to the Tomorrowland Foundation Music & Art School in Kolkata India together with @ektara.ngo. The chef made delicious traditional Belgian Waffles together with the girls from the school and his two sons, one of them (@luccav.d) also played a surprise DJ set. The Ek Tara NGO is working with children and women from impoverished families, aiming to provide high-quality holistic education to enable community transformation. All info: foundation.tomorrowland.com
